{"tid":986179,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拒寄十字架到澳門「矯枉過正」 香港順豐總經理「引咎辭職」","createTime":"2019-01-18T08:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T08:50:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"49f23ad419242667b27e452d129bdfea58bd32d3","tid":986179,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/01/20190118-CR-%E5%8D%81%E5%AD%97%E6%9E%B62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F01%2F20190118-CR-%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25AD%2597%25E6%259E%25B62.jpg&h=badb7a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順豐管理層對事件表示「不能理解和十分震驚」<br />\n<br />\n香港順豐繼昨晚致「萬分歉意」後，今日再發聲明，批評管理層未對工作人員進行相應培訓，「造成前線員工執行過度，矯枉過正」，順豐集團決定香港順豐總經理「立刻引咎辭職」。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，每個服務地區的收寄標準都必須符合目的地海關法律，調查發現管理層「未能充分理解上述法例依據，疏於對港順工作人員進行相應培訓，造成前線員工執行過度，矯枉過正」，令前線人員將宗教物品錯誤判斷為禁寄品，對事件表示「不能理解和十分震驚」。<br />\n<br />\n順豐稱會盡快針對有關情況，檢討並改善現時管理機制出現的問題，杜絕類似事件再次發生，集團對就事件「當事人和受到困擾的社會各界人士」致深切歉意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/3866997-%E6%8B%92%E5%AF%84%E5%8D%81%E5%AD%97%E6%9E%B6%E5%88%B0%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E5%BC%95%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A0%86%E8%B1%90%E7%B8%BD%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E5%BC%95%E5%92%8E%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7?current_cat=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F3866997-%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%25AF%2584%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25AD%2597%25E6%259E%25B6%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25BC%2595%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%25A0%2586%25E8%25B1%2590%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%2592%258E%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E8%2581%25B7%3Fcurrent_cat%3D1&d=099CS1sxW8vPw7uDUphh7R4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=233089c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/3866997-%E6%8B%92%E5%AF%84%E5%8D%81%E5%AD%97%E6%9E%B6%E5%88%B0%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E5%BC%95%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A0%86%E8%B1%90%E7%B8%BD%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E5%BC%95%E5%92%8E%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7?current_cat=1</a>"},{"pid":"f8668c83cd29a1e1e9077b32d684865aaa83efb4","tid":986179,"uid":113922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:48:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾sf 咩都唔運"},{"pid":"06b753023e36406db1ecdd622111963a8f865f59","tid":986179,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:49:43.000Z","msg":"【順豐審查】為拒寄十字架道歉 炒港區總經理「祭旗」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/985992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/985992</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"29afe7025ad53a60ca4511ce42ace35ab1ed128d","tid":986179,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"台灣個單呢,唔見你提下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}